From: Olaf Kirch <okir@suse.de>
Subject: Fix infinite loop in xfrm_lookup
References: 117749, 115200

It seems that the route xfrm_lookup is given on input can go
away when it sleeps.

Signed-off-by: Olaf Kirch <okir@suse.de>

